main event: A civilian reported a UFO sighting in Anchorage, Kentucky on March 22, 1967.
interesting points: The sighting lasted 50 seconds and was visually observed from the ground., The object was reported to be moving from south to north., The observer deemed the object to be unlike any known aircraft and not capable of carrying humanoids., No photographs or physical evidence were provided due to restrictions from the University Memorial., The conclusion of the report was that there was insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: A 49-year-old female who is widely read about UFOs and knows a little astronomy.
